rComments: DAVID IS AMAZING! One of the most kindest and down to earth professors ever. You can get an easy 80 in his class. Just do the readings, and understand what's going on and you'll be good. Quizzes are very hit or miss, so be careful. But David is a great guy. Fave!
Great Professor. Made the class experience absolutely amazing. Would take other courses with him in an instance. Probably my favorite teacher at UofT. Loved him.
tough but not always fair marker. Can come off as a bit harsh/judgmental.

You won't ever use the textbook. Or talk about the readings. When you go to see him about something, get ready to be insulted. Oh, and also - be prepared to have your GPA drop by about a letter grade.
Incredibly tough marker. He destroyed my confidence in just one class.
My favourite class of the term. He's excellent! Very interesting discussions, really shaking the boat and drawing up some debate. Great prof. Put in effort and you'll do well.
